sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Page as Page Component
    participant SWR as useSWR hook
    participant API as lib/api.ts
    participant Backend as FastAPI (localhost:8000)
    participant ErrorBoundary

    Note over User,ErrorBoundary: === 正常数据加载流程 ===

    User->>Page: 访问页面 (e.g. /)
    Page->>SWR: useSWR("strategies", api.getStrategies)

    alt 首次加载 (无缓存)
        SWR->>API: api.getStrategies()
        API->>API: get("/strategies")
        API->>Backend: GET /strategies<br/>headers: { X-API-Token }
        Backend-->>API: 200 OK [{...Strategy}]
        API-->>SWR: Strategy[]
        SWR-->>Page: { data: Strategy[], isLoading: false }
        Page->>User: 渲染策略列表
    else 缓存命中 + revalidate
        SWR-->>Page: { data: Strategy[] (stale), isValidating: true }
        Page->>User: 渲染缓存数据
        SWR->>API: api.getStrategies() (background)
        API->>Backend: GET /strategies
        Backend-->>API: 200 OK
        API-->>SWR: 新数据
        SWR-->>Page: 更新 data
        Page->>User: 重新渲染
    end

    Note over User,ErrorBoundary: === 错误处理流程 ===

    Page->>SWR: useSWR("strategies", api.getStrategies)
    SWR->>API: api.getStrategies()
    API->>Backend: GET /strategies
    Backend-->>API: 500 Internal Server Error
    API->>API: throw Error("GET /strategies failed: 500")
    API-->>SWR: Error thrown

    Note over SWR: SWRConfig: errorRetryCount=3, errorRetryInterval=5s

    loop 重试 3 次
        SWR->>API: 重试 api.getStrategies()
        API->>Backend: GET /strategies
        Backend-->>API: 500
    end

    SWR-->>Page: { error: Error("GET /strategies failed: 500"), data: undefined }
    Page->>User: 渲染 error 状态 (skeleton/fallback)

    Note over User,ErrorBoundary: === ErrorBoundary 降级流程 ===

    Page->>ErrorBoundary: 渲染包裹的子组件
    ErrorBoundary->>ErrorBoundary: 子组件渲染时 JS Error

    alt componentDidCatch 触发
        ErrorBoundary->>ErrorBoundary: getDerivedStateFromError(error)
        ErrorBoundary->>ErrorBoundary: componentDidCatch(error, errorInfo)
        ErrorBoundary->>User: 渲染 fallback UI<br/>(AlertTriangle + "组件加载失败" + 重试按钮)
    end

    User->>ErrorBoundary: 点击"重试"
    ErrorBoundary->>ErrorBoundary: handleReset() → setState({hasError: false})
    ErrorBoundary->>Page: 重新渲染子组件

    Note over User,ErrorBoundary: === 乐观更新流程 ===

    User->>Page: 点击"暂停"按钮 (策略启停)
    Page->>SWR: setStatus(id, "paused")
    SWR->>SWR: mutate(prev => prev.map(s => s.id===id ? {...s, status:"paused"} : s), {revalidate: false})
    SWR-->>Page: 立即更新 UI (乐观)
    SWR->>API: api.updateStrategyStatus(id, "paused")
    API->>Backend: PATCH /strategies/:id/status<br/>body: { status: "paused" }<br/>headers: { X-API-Token }
    Backend-->>API: 200 OK
    API-->>SWR: { id, status: "paused" }
    SWR->>Page: toast.success("策略已暂停")

    Note over User,ErrorBoundary: === 乐观更新失败回滚 ===

    SWR->>API: api.updateStrategyStatus(id, "stopped")
    API->>Backend: PATCH /strategies/:id/status
    Backend-->>API: 500 Error
    API-->>SWR: Error thrown
    SWR->>SWR: catch → mutate() (无条件 revalidate)
    SWR->>API: api.getStrategies() (重新拉取真实数据)
    SWR-->>Page: toast.error("操作失败，请重试") + 数据回滚
